data.text: @arcticninjapaul @joblocom Yeah I am interested in the casting but my assumption is they are going for the best people they can to make the films the best they can. I just read it and say "cool" now and then as I just want to see the film more than anything else!
@CoryMacRae @joblocom It’s just a casting announcement. Maybe you’re looking to deep? I’m certainly interested in SW casting.
@arcticninjapaul @joblocom Oh now I remember her! She is pretty good. Why is "good actress might be in Star Wars" a thing? If they cast me then yeah I can see it being a thing, but a good actress?
@CoryMacRae @joblocom She’s a good actress. In The Americans on F/X and used to be on Felicity. Was also great in Mission: Impossible 3. Now you can care.
@joblocom @arcticninjapaul Showing my ignorance, who is she, what has she done, why should I care?
